<br>
I have been playing this game for over 3 years now, and the most uber item I have ever bought was is my Emerald Dragonscale Breastplate for 10k.  I had to save like mad to get 10k to buy that breastplate.  Most of the other cool armor items I have on I got in raids, and a lot of them are NON-drop.<br>
<br>
So, this question came to mind...  Where the hell are you people getting all this plat????<br>
<br>
Did I miss the secret society note telling where the uber item drop camps are?  If I sold every single item I have on my character, I would be lucky to have 20k to my name.  So, how the hell does a person make 550k plat little alone 100k plat?  I admit, I am still a newb lamer even after 3 years of playing this game religously, but come on... if I saved every plat I ever make, it would still take me another 6 years or MORE to save 550k plat!!!<br>
<br>
Are there cheat codes and/or SoE employees giving money and items away to their buddies and I am the last person on Earth to realise it or what?????<br>
<br>
